    "name": "Kristala - Hallowed Lantern & Pyromaster Skull Helms",
    "steam_appid": 3274920,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/308158cb905db45c4761b410f957fb7c.avif?t=1730426824\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kristala is a dark fantasy ARPG featuring Sekiro-inspired combat, acrobatic parkour, and exploration to uncover a detailed story. Celebrate Kristaloween with our spooky, collector's helms, available to all players for a limited time in honor of Kristala's Chapter II release.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/5dcd2d1c77f947c04f9becfe45f0f536.webp?t=1730426824\" width=600 height=22 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > The Hallowed Lantern Helm</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On All Hallows' Eve, per Myr’s annual crypt-cleansing, Nisargans gather ‘round to whittle gourds and various root vegetables to frighten off wayward souls wandered from the Hallowed Haunts. A curious tradition adopted by all Anagativan clans.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A pumpkin carved in the likeness of a blazing ghoul—nicked by pranksters, no doubt.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/5d1ee58d4bb163365035930d7cb69e4e.poster.avif?t=1730426824\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/5d1ee58d4bb163365035930d7cb69e4e.webm?t=1730426824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/5d1ee58d4bb163365035930d7cb69e4e.mp4?t=1730426824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/5dcd2d1c77f947c04f9becfe45f0f536.webp?t=1730426824\" width=600 height=22 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Pyromaster Skull Helm </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“‘Tis better to burn the brightest than to fade a flame”, a Keozan proverb some pyromancers take all too literally.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The ever-burning skull of Pyromaster Romy, sifted from her ashes.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/9f394f25e27a008ab60bbd8eea7bd0f6.poster.avif?t=1730426824\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/9f394f25e27a008ab60bbd8eea7bd0f6.webm?t=1730426824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/9f394f25e27a008ab60bbd8eea7bd0f6.mp4?t=1730426824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/5dcd2d1c77f947c04f9becfe45f0f536.webp?t=1730426824\" width=600 height=22 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Both the Pyromaster Skull and Flaming Lantern helms are available to all players who already have Kristala in their library, and available to new players for a limited time following our Chapter II release.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/8ea68c12d47b39ee94e0272916b9a794.avif?t=1730426824\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras_big/8ea68c12d47b39ee94e0272916b9a794.avif?t=1730426824 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/b656ace893f12ef2ce4760417d01dfb3.avif?t=1730426824\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras_big/b656ace893f12ef2ce4760417d01dfb3.avif?t=1730426824 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
